origin.description:
Tom Scary (Tom Iansek of Big Scary and #1 Dads) remixes Jane Tyrrell's solo debut track Wild Waters.

Tom has upended the vocal hierarchy, highlighting breaths and backing vocals, setting them in a pulsing arrangement that expands on the sense of space in the original. The result is hypnotic.

Nailed it.

Tom Scary is the new moniker for Tom Iansek, to be applied when Iansek is wearing his producer hat. This is to distinguish him from his rapidly growing musical outpourings, as writer/front man for Big Scary and his solo project as #1 Dads. 
Coming from producing the Australian Music Prize winning “Not Art” for Big Scary, Tom Scary tries his hand at his first remix work, for Jane Tyrell’s “Wild Waters”.
